        h1 Lunar Landscapes of Lanzarote
        p For his 30th birthday, Dan wanted to escape winter and go in the Canaries. Can you blame him for wanting beautiful weather and a change of scenery? To be honest, I wasn’t that excited. All I’ve heard about Canary Islands was that it’s a turistic place full of english and german old people and there is nothing special about it. So, I tried to change his mind about it, but luckily did not succeed. Optimistic as he always is, he was convinced that we will find a place that both of us will like.Being faced with such a “brutal” enthusiasm the only thing that I could do is find a place that will make both of us happy. And we found it.

