      p This is a story about a captivating place, approximately 125 km off the coast of Africa. A place you would choose to see for various reasons: its arid volcanic landscapes, the wild and stunning beaches, the taste of a wine with a bit of an ash flavour, the small white villages washed by the Atlantic Ocean or situated in the middle of a black overwhelming landscape. It's the story of Lanzarote, an amazing island in the Canaries.

      h2.text-center Los Hervideros

      p Lanzarote welcomed us with a jaw-dropping spectacle of nature : the ocean waves dramatically whipping the bizarre-shaped cliffs and force water into the labyrinth of caves. This is “Los Hervideros”, a breathtaking place in so many different ways. It is our favourite place from the island and words are not enough.

